      • setTableColumnWidthPercentages

        public void setTableColumnWidthPercentages(javax.swing.JTable table,
                                           double[] percentages)
        Set the width of the columns as percentages.
        Parameters:
        table - the JTable whose columns will be set
        percentages - the widths of the columns as percentages

        Note: this method does NOT verify that all percentages add up to 100% and for the columns to appear properly, it is recommended that the widths for ALL columns be specified.
